page.name: Eulin II
page.description: Lightning Caller. The Spark of Brilliance. Alone in the storm, he held the line against a horde of invading elementals and came out unscathed. He is... Eulin II.

properties.name: Eulin II
properties.description: Lightning Caller. The Spark of Brilliance. Alone in the storm, he held the line against a horde of invading elementals and came out unscathed. He is... Eulin II.
properties.complete: And so the Champion of the Lagohm has met his match. Luckily for him, he's still quite cute. Also he's fine, don't worry. Nothing a good nap won't take care of.

page.name: Lagohm Chargelance
page.description: A spectacular recreation of a shocking Lagohm-tech antique! Although Lagohm society puts progress on a pedestal, the likes of the Champion's own creations has never since been seen. Proof of victory over Eulin II! (Cosmetic)
